      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为Module 14画一个时序图，主题是Soft Delete，属于Security_ZeroTrust安全框架的一部分。核心场景是临床工程师通过Azure Backup Vault来保护Workload VM的数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Module 14",
        "Soft Delete",
        "Security_ZeroTrust",
        "Clinical Engineer",
        "Azure Backup Vault",
        "Workload VM"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，三个参与者：Clinical Engineer、Azure Backup Vault、Workload VM。流程上是不是先由临床工程师配置策略，然后Azure去触发备份作业？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Clinical Engineer",
        "Azure Backup Vault",
        "Workload VM",
        "Configure policy",
        "Trigger snapshot/backup job"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，第一步是ClinEng向Azure Backup Vault发送配置策略的指令。然后Azure作为中间协调者，去触发Workload VM上的快照或备份作业。这里用虚线箭头表示异步触发。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ClinEng",
        "Azure",
        "Configure policy",
        "Trigger snapshot/backup job"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经画好了前两步交互。那备份完成后，数据流怎么走？Workload VM需要把恢复点传回给Azure Backup Vault吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Workload VM",
        "Azure Backup Vault",
        "Send recovery point"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，Workload完成备份后，把恢复点传回Azure存储。最后一步是临床工程师要验证这个恢复点，查看报告，确认备份成功且符合合规要求。这是Soft Delete机制的前置流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Workload",
        "Azure",
        "Send recovery point",
        "ClinEng",
        "Validate recovery point & reports",
        "Soft Delete"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "验证环节我理解为ClinEng主动查询Azure Backup Vault，获取恢复点状态和报告。这样整个闭环就完整了：配置→触发→上传→验证。标题我定为\"Module 14 – Soft Delete (Security_ZeroTrust)\"，可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Module 14 – Soft Delete (Security_ZeroTrust)",
        "ClinEng-Azure",
        "Validate recovery point & reports"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "标题没问题。不过我想再确认一下箭头的样式：配置和验证都是实线箭头，因为是指令操作；触发备份和回传恢复点用虚线箭头，因为是异步事件。这样区分更清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Configure policy",
        "Validate recovery point & reports",
        "Trigger snapshot/backup job",
        "Send recovery point"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整完成。实线用于ClinEng到Azure的主动操作，虚线用于Azure与Workload之间的异步数据流。整个时序图现在完整呈现了Soft Delete场景下，临床工程师如何通过ZeroTrust机制完成工作负载的备份与验证流程。",
